item.title: CVE-2023-2888|2023-10-23T07:04:50.673Z -- n%2Fa -- phpok
item.description: A vulnerability, which was classified as problematic, was found in PHPOK 6.4.100. This affects an unknown part of the file /admin.php?c=upload&f=zip&_noCache=0.1683794968. The manipulation leads to unrestricted upload. It is possible to initiate the attack remotely. The identifier VDB-229953 was assigned to this vulnerability.
